'''''Play It Now''''' is an album by saxophonist [[Al Cohn]] which was recorded in 1975 and released on the [[Xanadu Records|Xanadu]] label.<ref>[http://www.jazzlists.com/SJ_Label_Xanadu.htm Xanadu Records discography] accessed May 1, 2014</ref>
==Reception==
{{Album ratings
| rev1 = ''[[Allmusic]]''
| rev1Score = {{rating|3|5}}<ref name="Allmusic"/> 
|rev2 = ''[[The Rolling Stone Jazz Record Guide]]''
| rev2Score = {{rating|5|5}}<ref name=RSJRG> {{Cite book
 |editor-last=Swenson
